Magandang trabaho.

00:44:10.419 --> 00:44:12.421
PULISYA MILITAR

00:44:25.142 --> 00:44:26.519
Isa, dalawa.

00:44:26.602 --> 00:44:27.853
Isa, dalawa.

00:44:35.611 --> 00:44:37.905
Tingnan mo itong maliit na kalokohan.
Nakaiwas ka lang ba?

00:44:40.074 --> 00:44:41.325
Susmaryosep. / Susmaryosep.

00:44:41.409 --> 00:44:43.369
Paano mo hinayaan na mangyari ito?

00:44:43.452 --> 00:44:44.453
Pasensya na po, ginoo!

00:44:44.537 --> 00:44:47.290
Pareho nating trabaho ang nakataya
kung hindi natin ito mapipigilan.

00:44:47.373 --> 00:44:48.833
-Naririnig mo ba ako?
-Opo, ginoo!

00:44:48.916 --> 00:44:51.669
